  <!-- EN: Zone core -->
  <QE_ZoneCore.label>区域核心</QE_ZoneCore.label>
  <!-- EN: Zone core is a tool for designing custom maps, which can be used to generate "map parts". When generating a custom map, if there is a zone core on the map, it will extract the "map parts" based on its settings for generation. -->
  <QE_ZoneCore.description>区域核心是一种用于设计自定义地图的工具，可用于生成“地图部分”。生成自定义地图时，如果地图上有区域核心，它将根据其设置挑选出“地图部分”以进行生成。</QE_ZoneCore.description>
  
